RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: enlistee
<hw>enlistee</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>any new member of an
organization or supporter of a cause.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> recruit.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>an enlisted man or woman in the armed
forces.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>a person who enlisted voluntarily in the armed
forces; -- contrasted with <contr>draftee</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>enlisting</ent>⟦br⟧
